<div class="help-content-wrap"><h3 id="how-to-register">How to Register</h3>
<ol>
<li><p>To register a SportyBet Ghana account please visit www.sportybet.com and click on the “Register” button on the top-right of the Home page.</p>
</li>
<li><p>Fill in the form with your phone number and password to create an account, or log in with Facebook.</p>
</li>
<li><p>You will receive a Verification Code via SMS. Please enter the correct code on the next page and tap on &quot;Complete Registration&quot;.</p>
</li>
<li><p>You are ready to start playing! Please enter your username and password to log into your account.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>